{"tid":753153,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅行相] 東京，江之島，橫濱","createTime":"2018-07-23T11:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T14:13:02.000Z","uid":38569,"like":26,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ba444b1c1e21e406fdd44da004e116ce775123b3","tid":753153,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"七月頭去咗東京 影咗都唔少相<br />\n決定開個post highlight吓去咗嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都喺旅遊台開咗遊記 有興趣可以嚟呢度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/753142/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/753142/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">之前嘅Posts:<br />\n九洲:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/520469/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/520469/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/525126/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/525126/page/1</a><br />\n沙巴:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/712781/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/712781/page/1</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n大約講吓帶咗啲咩Gear:<br />\n- Sony A7 (一代 影相其實都非常夠其實 不過用電子Adaptor反應就好慢)<br />\n- FE55 (snapshot 影街景都ok 不過全開近攝散景有啲旋 睇個人喜好啦)<br />\n- Canon 1740L (貪平，連個Viltrox adaptor都係4000，不過A7一代嘅自動對焦係慢到用唔到)<br />\n- FE24240 (天涯鏡，不過焦段咁廣嘅弊病就係變形幾犀利吓 水平要控制得好好，枝鏡亦都好重，後期棄咗冇用)<br />\n- Rolleicord VB (最後影咗一卷Portra 400，差唔多兩卷Provia 100F)<br />\n<br />\n有興趣不妨去Follow IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tay.wong_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftay.wong_%2F&d=aYSZWfyDJHTTrJhvohPP0CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=57f703f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tay.wong_/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>街景</ins></strong></span><br />\n去到東京當然要影吓街景<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>新宿街頭</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191511_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191511_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg&h=2fa1820f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191511_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191511_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg&h=3825f247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191511_f99687dd719c4e8bc6a39e946c3d9ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191511_f99687dd719c4e8bc6a39e946c3d9ef7.jpg&h=76322fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191512_2de40e0d504f583cda7465979f958a98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191512_2de40e0d504f583cda7465979f958a98.jpg&h=1c0f139d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191512_135007e7085979a7d5b41ce54c0e54d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191512_135007e7085979a7d5b41ce54c0e54d7.jpg&h=80f3049a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>思い出横丁</ins></strong><br />\n咁啱行過都好出名吓嘅地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191537_fac4ef5554f69012fe38d2f1d4e245a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191537_fac4ef5554f69012fe38d2f1d4e245a6.jpg&h=ae039214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191538_e4bde0eb46b8f32ef4b4207f5344b4d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191538_e4bde0eb46b8f32ef4b4207f5344b4d4.jpg&h=524e1f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191538_86c3cbc8cde622a8c725d89a88bdcb96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191538_86c3cbc8cde622a8c725d89a88bdcb96.jpg&h=8ae0b55d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191538_1058abae0dc372f4432cbea7fa123512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191538_1058abae0dc372f4432cbea7fa123512.jpg&h=c8298006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>其他</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191556_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191556_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg&h=c8814e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191557_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191557_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg&h=a38a7908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191557_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191557_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg&h=986d6a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/191557_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F191557_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg&h=50b4c235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7fa8db9576620320bfea5dd37685ab1856bb839","tid":753153,"uid":33733,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"有冇後期執過<br />\n想知點先影到呢種效