s></strong></span><br />\n平時香港好少影<br />\n去旅行嗰陣通常都比較放膽去影<br />\n雖然感覺都仲係重構圖色彩多過故事<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192021_134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192021_134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b723.jpg&h=9b2aac16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新宿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192030_648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192030_648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec.jpg&h=554f96e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀座<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192039_adaf0ad2e085c835a82b2f021fe236ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192039_adaf0ad2e085c835a82b2f021fe236ae.jpg&h=22ede839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192042_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192042_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg&h=8289f686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n築地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192055_eb935669c45405844c35aafbd5fe43d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192055_eb935669c45405844c35aafbd5fe43d7.jpg&h=a99cb367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇等到最多人嘅時段先嚟影<br />\n對旅行嚟講好事 但對影相嚟講就差少少特色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192108_e0e28452229af52e70f87dd03c3a30c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192108_e0e28452229af52e70f87dd03c3a30c2.jpg&h=f53d43ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192108_129e458698c4745a32d44582161b51d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192108_129e458698c4745a32d44582161b51d8.jpg&h=da280033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192108_e25418821200a0f7c8f9f81b22d21691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192108_e25418821200a0f7c8f9f81b22d21691.jpg&h=22e1587b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江之島天王祭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192117_e3e6f22244e557f1758d397a98734145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192117_e3e6f22244e557f1758d397a98734145.jpg&h=bed059a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橫濱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/192127_f0d0b070be593820651230120b0374be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F192127_f0d0b070be593820651230120b0374be.jpg&h=9ed89b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淺草寺祈福人士"},{"pid":"73d4fdffd933e12708b48d583f6b00e3df641960","tid":753153,"uid":50502,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"d 相影得幾好 調色整柒哂"},{"pid":"c5be1716b0575f7d3c2177147fde95ea27b841dd","tid":753153,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"可否用黎做我wallpaper"},{"pid":"d81fcbad6f20656669189f08eceae3d60958f552","tid":753153,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73d4fdffd933e12708b48d583f6b00e3df641960","tid":753153,"uid":50502,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"d 相影得幾好 調色整柒哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"例如邊啲 求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e136d24ecb392868d94fac2d4aae78f49cbb63","tid":753153,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5be1716b0575f7d3c2177147fde95ea27b841dd","tid":753153,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"可否用黎做我wallpaper"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"可以呀 冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597fe04422fb024c44a38459aaeb16b9ebc27318","tid":753153,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"冇人討論 完埋個post佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>景點</ins></strong></span><br />\n有兩度地方好似都唔係特別Popular同多人去<br />\n放幾張相介紹吓<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>八景島海島公園</ins></strong><br />\n去開橫濱又諗唔到去邊可以考慮吓<br />\n大約50分鐘車程<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201249_853b031a43495200d111d6f5239398a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201249_853b031a43495200d111d6f5239398a3.jpg&h=5a8aa28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201250_daa79432b242c16e82493597a4d8c41f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201250_daa79432b242c16e82493597a4d8c41f.jpg&h=a25294be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201250_fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201250_fed1da6da79ca8f0cba2aa0c88e14d9e.jpg&h=343fb633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201250_b21f0bedce1dfeee7e158f1a8888beab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201250_b21f0bedce1dfeee7e158f1a8888beab.jpg&h=b71b5115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201251_1f9ffafcc4c0bbc70331f044b842b7fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201251_1f9ffafcc4c0bbc70331f044b842b7fc.jpg&h=068db679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201251_9bca1653601cfed0253482a381c1ad63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201251_9bca1653601cfed0253482a381c1ad63.jpg&h=41ba4fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最好早啲去 因為嗰陣係星期一開場時間所以第一張相好好彩可以慢慢等Subject同構圖<br />\n不過差唔多晏晝嘅時候已經好多細路同旅客<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>六義園</ins></strong><br />\n東京駒込站附近嘅日式庭園 閒日嘅晏晝去到<br />\n可以因為太熱 人唔多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201311_9371882dcce45ee625a0ce0ba5d0b81d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201311_9371882dcce45ee625a0ce0ba5d0b81d.jpg&h=dea7409c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201311_cd0d165e9302c73978d21d8cbf01c48a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201311_cd0d165e9302c73978d21d8cbf01c48a.jpg&h=52b52ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201311_c7588853d975607658e9c3a1aa5a0dc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201311_c7588853d975607658e9c3a1aa5a0dc0.jpg&h=5cb3080a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201312_fd107bec4a5eaaed6441a46280dcc929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201312_fd107bec4a5eaaed6441a46280dcc929.jpg&h=e172a001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201312_cf5d3c0bfc6069452f2473d6904da38b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201312_cf5d3c0bfc6069452f2473d6904da38b.jpg&h=8753e495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201312_4f7fcc45033f46b53db98b6c7db082d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201312_4f7fcc45033f46b53db98b6c7db082d7.jpg&h=7be41062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>百合海鷗號 (Yurikamome)</ins></strong><br />\n嚴格嚟講都唔算係一個景點<br />\n不過係一條花啲時間搭吓嘅線 尤其係順路去台場嘅話<br />\n條線有咩咁特別? 就係經過彩虹橋 好適合去影埋timelapse<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201332_9876c9a3f300f29c8ee619765c1ad768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201332_9876c9a3f300f29c8ee619765c1ad768.jpg&h=3d045281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201332_32a03ccfe376e30cb0a7f869918353e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201332_32a03ccfe376e30cb0a7f869918353e8.jpg&h=fb79b7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201332_550319b866c18a57d557d61167728919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201332_550319b866c18a57d557d61167728919.jpg&h=53ef0828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201333_217479a24f5b98bcd9028a1675b0f69e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201333_217479a24f5b98bcd9028a1675b0f69e.jpg&h=8e52e011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>風景</ins></strong></span><br />\n今次trip去到河口湖天氣太差乜都冇去<br />\n影嘅大景唔算太多<br />\n所以滿意嘅相都唔多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201744_3f93da36e4dcc70910e18ac429cf2a3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201744_3f93da36e4dcc70910e18ac429cf2a3c.jpg&h=3786af7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201745_cf0a5dcb4ca3264bc8a7c6c4f31cc65f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201745_cf0a5dcb4ca3264bc8a7c6c4f31cc65f.jpg&h=0a6e6afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201745_615f58a4072d525b89081fc1b6b6382a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201745_615f58a4072d525b89081fc1b6b6382a.jpg&h=53df47c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201745_3571adc2900d18ca7bbb29ffef49e706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201745_3571adc2900d18ca7bbb29ffef49e706.jpg&h=eacf056f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201746_baaf94542a40d7deb9a8a917acb1b150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201746_baaf94542a40d7deb9a8a917acb1b150.jpg&h=72f131ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201746_5f5f96e221fee78568ec8daee175f851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F201746_5f5f96e221fee78568ec8daee175f851.jpg&h=0fc37531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/201746_db8e74df8d74f3efdd249a3fd3a466da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23